📖 Project Overview
This project is a Tribute Page dedicated to Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam (1931–2015), the former President of India and one of the country's most respected scientists. The webpage highlights his image, a famous quote, and a brief biography in a visually appealing and responsive layout.

The project is built using HTML and CSS and demonstrates fundamental web development concepts such as page structure, styling, responsive design, and image integration.

✨ Features
Responsive and user-friendly design
Vibrant gradient background
Glassmorphism-style content container
Tribute heading with birth and death years
Local image of Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam
Famous inspirational quote
Brief biography section
Mobile-friendly layout

🛠️ Technologies Used
HTML5
CSS3

