🖼️ Using a Local Image
Place the image of Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam inside the images folder and update the image source in index.html:
<img src="images/kalam.jpg" alt="A.P.J. Abdul Kalam">

🚀 How to Run the Project
Download or clone the repository.
Ensure the image file is stored in the images folder.
Open index.html in any web browser.
View the tribute page.

