🌟 About Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam
Dr. A.P.J. Abdul Kalam was an eminent scientist, educator, and the 11th President of India. Known as the "Missile Man of India", he played a significant role in India's space and missile development programs. His dedication to education, innovation, and national development continues to inspire millions around the world.

